  <entry>
    <title>github-hexo搭建博客</title>
    <link href="https://huangchao.com/2020/12/15/github-hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"/>
    <id>https://huangchao.com/2020/12/15/github-hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</id>
    <published>2020-12-14T18:14:50.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-12-14T18:14:50.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="我的hexo博客"><a href="#我的hexo博客" class="headerlink" title="我的hexo博客"></a><a href="https://qqnv.github.io/">我的hexo博客</a></h1><h2 id="一、安装git"><a href="#一、安装git" class="headerlink" title="一、安装git"></a>一、安装git</h2><h2 id="二、安装node-js"><a href="#二、安装node-js" class="headerlink" title="二、安装node.js"></a>二、安装node.js</h2><h2 id="三、命令行依次执行"><a href="#三、命令行依次执行" class="headerlink" title="三、命令行依次执行"></a>三、命令行依次执行</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br><span class="line">hexo init blog</span><br><span class="line">cd blog</span><br><span class="line">npm install</span><br><span class="line">hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>出现<strong>图示1</strong>即安装成功，blog即为新创建的博客文件夹，登陆图示网址即可本地访问<br><img src="https://cdn.qqnv.com/hexo1.png" alt="图示1"></p><h2 id="四、连接git的准备"><a href="#四、连接git的准备" class="headerlink" title="四、连接git的准备"></a>四、连接git的准备</h2><ul><li>命令行执行ssh-keygen -t rsa -C “邮件地址@youremail.com”在本地生成新的 SSH Key</li><li>在本地文件夹找到id_rsa.pub文件并打开复制里面的内容,进入GitHub主页，进入settings，左侧选SSH and GPG keys，将复制的内容粘贴到对应位置，title随便填个</li><li>命令行执行ssh-T <a href="mailto:&#x67;&#x69;&#116;&#64;&#x67;&#x69;&#x74;&#104;&#117;&#98;&#46;&#x63;&#x6f;&#109;">&#x67;&#x69;&#116;&#64;&#x67;&#x69;&#x74;&#104;&#117;&#98;&#46;&#x63;&#x6f;&#109;</a>提示<strong>图示2</strong>即为成功<img src="https://cdn.qqnv.com/hexo2.png" alt="图示2"></li><li>命令行执行git config –global user.name “username”//输入注册时的username</li><li>命令行执行git config –global user.email  “<a href="mailto:&#121;&#x6f;&#117;&#x72;&#110;&#97;&#109;&#x65;&#x40;&#x79;&#x6f;&#117;&#x72;&#109;&#x61;&#x69;&#108;&#x2e;&#x63;&#111;&#x6d;">&#121;&#x6f;&#117;&#x72;&#110;&#97;&#109;&#x65;&#x40;&#x79;&#x6f;&#117;&#x72;&#109;&#x61;&#x69;&#108;&#x2e;&#x63;&#111;&#x6d;</a>“//填写注册邮箱</li><li>创建GitHub仓库，仓库必须为username.github.io</li></ul><h2 id="五、配置blog文件夹中的-config-yml文件"><a href="#五、配置blog文件夹中的-config-yml文件" class="headerlink" title="五、配置blog文件夹中的_config.yml文件"></a>五、配置blog文件夹中的_config.yml文件</h2><p>  按照<strong>图示3、4</strong>依次配置<br><img src="https://cdn.qqnv.com/hexo3.png" alt="图示3"><br><img src="https://cdn.qqnv.com/hexo4.png" alt="图示4"></p><h2 id="六、连接到GitHub"><a href="#六、连接到GitHub" class="headerlink" title="六、连接到GitHub"></a>六、连接到GitHub</h2><p>cd到blog文件夹下，命令行依次执行</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="七、登陆username-github-io即可访问"><a href="#七、登陆username-github-io即可访问" class="headerlink" title="七、登陆username.github.io即可访问"></a>七、登陆username.github.io即可访问</h2><h2 id="八、更换主题"><a href="#八、更换主题" class="headerlink" title="八、更换主题"></a>八、更换主题</h2><ul><li>去GitHub上下载想要的主题放在themes目录下</li><li>更改_config.yml中的theme属性为下载的主题文件夹名</li><li>返回主目录命令行依次执行</li></ul><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo generate</span><br><span class="line">hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>等待一分钟刷新页面即可</p><h2 id="九、更改本地数据"><a href="#九、更改本地数据" class="headerlink" title="九、更改本地数据"></a>九、更改本地数据</h2><p>命令行执行cd到blog目录下，依次执行</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean（清除缓存）</span><br><span class="line">hexo g（生成）</span><br><span class="line">hexo s（启动本地服务，进行文章预览调试，退出服务用Ctrl+c）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="十、Hexo命令行常用命令"><a href="#十、Hexo命令行常用命令" class="headerlink" title="十、Hexo命令行常用命令"></a>十、Hexo命令行常用命令</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-cli -g（Hexo安装）</span><br><span class="line">hexo init blog（Hexo第一个项目博客）</span><br><span class="line">cd blog（cd到blog目录下）</span><br><span class="line">npm install（安装依赖包）</span><br><span class="line">hexo server（启动本地服务器，开启预览访问端口（默认端口4000，&#x27;ctrl + c&#x27;关闭server））</span><br><span class="line">hexo new &quot;postName&quot; （新建文章）</span><br><span class="line">hexo new page &quot;pageName&quot; （新建页面）</span><br><span class="line">hexo generate （生成静态页面至public目录）</span><br><span class="line">hexo deploy （部署到GitHub）</span><br><span class="line">hexo help （查看帮助）</span><br><span class="line">hexo version （查看Hexo的版本）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>缩写：</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo n == hexo new</span><br><span class="line">hexo g == hexo generate</span><br><span class="line">hexo s == hexo server</span><br><span class="line">hexo d == hexo deploy</span><br><span class="line">hexo s -g（生成本地预览）</span><br><span class="line">hexo d -g（生成并上传）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p style="color:red">注：本文中所有username即为自己的GitHub注册名</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
